Ark,is,an,email,search,and,people,search,application,Ark,provides,an,email,application,that,compiles,all,social,information,about,contacts,and,provides,a,social,search,engine,for,people,and,contacts,The,Ark,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Ark,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Public,documentation,is,not,available,interested,developers,should,request,an,API,key,here,http,ark,com,beta,api